{
  "stem": "22582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was the only one who was very Jewish looking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the family decided to let her go on errant papers and send her to friends, to Warsaw somewhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But meanwhile, as she was shook whenever they-- they-- they found her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some kind they wanted money that she's Jewish, shaking up with money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as long as she had money, she was giving.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But later, she didn't have money, so they-- she was denounced.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she put-- she was put on the train to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she jumped the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she was all blooded from the-- from when she jumped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she came back to-- to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She went right to the arbeitsamt which was workplace, when they were sending people to Germany-- the Poles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So she said she's volunteering to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she wants to escape from the family who are very, very Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she's pro-- pro-German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so that's how she got into Germany as a-- as a Polish girl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she was working for a German family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then she-- she-- then she changed places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she went to another German family, which were very prominent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "An engineer who was working on the V1 and V2, which was sent to England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, like missiles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Missiles.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The first missiles actually were developed by Germans, and they were the one that she was-- she was serving the old big shots of Germany hierarchy in their home.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she-- he was a Nazi, but he loved her, because she-- they didn't have children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was very nice, and she spoke German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was saying that she was a pro-German, and she was a this, and she had to-- because it was very strange that she didn't have any correspondence with her family.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
